  "intent": "Execute GeneRead QIAact Lung DNA UMI Panel target enrichment PCR by preparing forward and reverse master mixes containing TE-PCR buffer (4\u00b5L per sample), primers (5\u00b5L per sample), TE-PCR primer mix (0.8\u00b5L per sample), and DNA polymerase (0.8\u00b5L per sample) at 4\u00b0C. Distribute 10.6\u00b5L of each master mix to PCR tubes containing DNA libraries, mix 7 times with 10\u00b5L volume, then transfer 20\u00b5L reactions to thermocycler plate. Run thermal cycling protocol: 95\u00b0C for 13 minutes, 98\u00b0C for 2 minutes, followed by 8 cycles of 98\u00b0C for 15 seconds and 68\u00b0C for 10 minutes, with final extension at 72\u00b0C for 5 minutes.",
